oming Out This Week</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">April 7, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/crimereads/">CrimeReads </a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/david-handler-interview/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/04/81GIlls866L._SL1500_-2-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/david-handler-interview/">Point of Origin: David Handler on Flashing Back to the Beginnings of Hoagy, Lulu & Friends</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">April 5, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/johnvaleri/">John B. Valeri</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/a-quest-for-a-loyal-dracula-adaptation/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/04/Dracula-reading-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/a-quest-for-a-loyal-dracula-adaptation/">A Quest for a Loyal <em>Dracula</em> Adaptation</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">April 4, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/oliviarutigliano/">Olivia Rutigliano</a></span></div></li></ul></li>
